➜乌克兰举行“世界清洁日”废弃物服装走秀
http://www.sohu.com/a/419989691_114731	3429
<p><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200922/03b78a41da364ec6a74b720654ef2243.jpeg" /></p>
